title: 1929 Crime - Love's Conquest - Robert Armstrong, Carole Lombard, Roland Drew

sources.title: 1929 Crime - Love's Conquest - Robert Armstrong, Carole Lombard, Roland Drew
sources.description:
New York City gangster Mahlon Keene (Robert Armstrong) melts when he meets down-on-her-luck beauty Rhoda (Carole Lombard), a society gal who's in desperate need of dough to support herself and her boyfriend, Tony (Roland Drew), a brilliant violinist with a serious drinking problem. Mahlon pulls some strings to help Tony get back on top; in return, Rhoda is to dump the musician and marry the mobster. The already heated situation is further complicated when the cops decide to crack down on Mahlon.

Original title: The Racketeer (1929)
Directed by Howard Higgin

Main cast:
Robert Armstrong - Mahlon Keane
Carole Lombard - Rhoda Philbrooke
Roland Drew - Tony Vaughan
Paul Hurst - Mehaffy, Policeman
Kit Guard - Gus
Al Hill - Squid
Bobby Dunn - The Rat
Budd Fine - Bernie Weber
Hedda Hopper - Mrs. Karen Lee
Jeanette Loff - Millie Chapman
John Loder - Jack Oakhurst
Winter Hall as Mr. Sam Chapman
Winifred Harris - Mrs. Margaret Chapman
